<section id="about" class="about t__section">
    <div class="about__more">
        <div class="t__container">
            <h2 class="t__typedivider">About me</h2>
            <p class="t__lead">In the ever-evolving digital design landscape, I found my passion for crafting meaningful experiences that bridge the gap between users and technology. My journey began with a deep-rooted curiosity for design and technology, leading me down a path where creativity meets functionality.</p>
            <p>As a product designer, I wear many hats - from envisioning sleek interfaces to delving into the intricacies of programming. Each project is an opportunity to weave my expertise in web standards with an innate sense of aesthetics, creating immersive experiences that captivate and inspire.</p>
            <p>Collaboration lies at the heart of my process. I thrive in dynamic environments where ideas flow freely, working closely with product teams to decipher business goals while keeping a keen eye on customer needs. Immersed in a world of constant innovation, I find solace in the meticulous nature of research, partnering with researchers to uncover insights that drive design decisions.</p>
            <p>Accessibility is not just a checkbox for me; it's a guiding principle that shapes every aspect of my work. I believe in creating inclusive designs catering to all users, ensuring every interaction is seamless and intuitive.</p>
            <p>My portfolio speaks volumes of my dedication to excellence. From intricate data visualizations to elegant design systems, I've had the privilege of bringing visions to life and establishing three successful multi-brand design systems - one meticulously crafted from scratch.</p>
            <p>Driven by a relentless pursuit of perfection, I enjoy the intricate dance between creativity and functionality. With every project, I strive to push the boundaries of what's possible, leaving a lasting impression on users and stakeholders alike.</p>
            <p>In the realm of digital design, the journey is never-ending, and I am excited to embark on the next chapter, where innovation knows no bounds and possibilities are limitless.</p>
            {% if skills %}
                <h3>My skills</h3>
                <div class="about__skills">    
                    {% for skill in skills %}
                        <div class="about__skills__group">
                            <h4 class="h6">
                                {% include 'skills/' + skill.title | slug + '.svg' %}
                                <strong>{{ skill.title }}</strong>
                            </h4>
                            <ul>
                                {% for child in skill.body %}
                                    <li>{{ child }}</li>
                                {% endfor %}
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
    {% if reads %}
        <div class="about__reads">
            <div class="t__container">
                <h3>Favorite readings</h3>
                <p>My reading habits tend to ebb and flow. There are phases where I devour multiple books within a month, and then there are times when a single book captivates me for months. Here's a compilation of recommended reads from my literary journey:</p>
            </div>
            <ol class="t__inline">
                {% for read in reads %}
                    <li class="t__inline__item t__inline__item--1">
                        <a class="t__hover t__hover--2" href="{{ read.link | url }}" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank" title="{{ read.title }} by {{ read.author}}">
                            {% book 'src/static/books/' + read.title | slug + '.jpg', read.title %}
                        </a>
                    </li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ol>
        </div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if software %}
        <div class="about__software">
            <div class="t__container">
                <h3>Software I use</h3>
                <p>These are the applications that seamlessly integrate into my daily routine, becoming indispensable tools I rely on day in and day out. They facilitate my productivity, creativity, and communication, allowing me to navigate various tasks with efficiency and finesse:</p>
                <ol class="t__inline">
                    {% for app in software %}
                        <li class="t__inline__item t__inline__item--1">
                            <a class="t__hover t__hover--2" href="{{ app.link | url }}" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank" title="{{ app.title }}">
                                {% include 'software/' + app.title | slug + '.svg' %}
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if hardware %}
        <div class="about__hardware">
            <div class="t__container">
                <h3>Hardware I use</h3>
                <p>Behold the arsenal of tools that form the backbone of my creative endeavors. These are the instruments that consistently accompany me in the pursuit of crafting excellence:</p>
                <ul class="link-style">
                    {% for gadget in hardware %}
                        <li>
                            <a href="{{ gadget.link | url }}" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">{{ gadget.title }}</a>
                        </li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    {% endif %}
    <div class="about__bits">
        <div class="t__container">
            <h3>My latest bits</h3>
            <p>A glimpse into my career journey reveals a diverse spectrum of projects I've had the privilege to engage with. These undertakings span various industries and creative challenges.</p>
            <p><small>Detailed information about these projects is readily <a href="#contact" title="Go to the Contact section">available uppon request</a>.</small></p>
        </div>
        <ol class="t__grid t__grid--works">
            {% for work in collections.work %}
                {% if work.url == false %}
                    <li class="t__grid__item">
                        <article class="t__card">
                            <header class="t__card__header">
                                <h4 class="t__card__title">{{ work.data.title }}</h4>
                                {% if work.data.client %}
                                    <p class="t__card__client">{{ work.data.client }}</p>
                                {% elif work.data.nft %}
                                    <span class="t__card__client">NFT</span>
                                {% endif %}
                                {% if work.data.description %}
                                    <p class="t__card__desc">{{ work.data.description }}</p>
                                {% endif %}
                            </header>
                            {% thumbnail work.data.thumbnail, work.data.title %}
                        </article>
                    </li>
                {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
        </ol>
    </div>
    <div class="about__website">
        <div class="t__container">
            <h3>About this website <sup>Nerd Zone</sup></h3>
            <ul class="link-style">
                <li>Uses a several typefaces:
                    <ul class="link-style">
                        <li><a href="https://processtypefoundry.com/fonts/colfax/" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Colfax</a> and <a href="https://processtypefoundry.com/fonts/klavika-display/" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Klavika Display</a> by Process Type Foundry.</li>
                        <li><a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Caveat#about" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Caveat</a> by Impallari Type.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>This page scores ~98 of 100 on <a href="https://pagespeed.web.dev/report?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhoroman.com%2F" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">PageSpeed Insights</a>.</li>
                <li>The theme of this website dynamically adjusts in response to your operating system's colour scheme.</li>
                <li>Powered by <a href="https://11ty.dev" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">11ty</a> as static site generator, JavaScript, SASS and Nunjucks.</li>
                <li>Hosted using <a href="https://pages.github.com" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">GitHub Pages</a> and <a href="https://github.com/features/actions" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">GitHub Actions</a>.</li>
                <li>This website doesn't use any cookies.</li>
                <li><a href="https://splitbee.io" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Slitbee</a> is used as analytics platform.</li>
                <li>Current site version is {{ site.version }}.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
